#. hb : P bâ‚پ bâ‚‚
#. ```
#: Game.Doc.Tactic
msgid ""
"آ§0 is equivalent to آ§1: the tactic replaces an assumption\n"
"آ§2 with the special case آ§3.\n"
"\n"
"If you want to specialize multiple times, instead of آ§4 you should use آ§5,\n"
"since آ§6 overwrites the old assumption آ§7.\n"
"From the above assumption آ§8, you can obtain the following three assumptions "
"with\n"
"آ§9\n"
":\n"
"آ§10"
msgstr ""

